{"id":8197,"date":"2026-02-03T11:12:53","date_gmt":"2026-02-03T04:12:53","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/?p=8197"},"modified":"2026-02-03T11:12:53","modified_gmt":"2026-02-03T04:12:53","slug":"allantoin-hoat-chat-lam-diu-phuc-hoi","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/su-kien\/allantoin-hoat-chat-lam-diu-phuc-hoi\/","title":{"rendered":"Allantoin \u2013 Ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t l\u00e0m d\u1ecbu &amp; ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o cho da"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">\u00a0Allantoin xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u trong m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m d\u01b0\u1ee1ng \u1ea9m, h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 k\u00edch \u1ee9ng nh\u1eb9, ch\u0103m s\u00f3c sau treatment. Nh\u1ecf b\u00e9, n\u1ec1n t\u00ednh, nh\u01b0ng khi c\u1ea7n gi\u1ea3m \u0111\u1ecf r\u00e1t hay l\u00e0m \u00eam c\u00f4ng th\u1ee9c ch\u1ee9a actives m\u1ea1nh \u00eam h\u01a1n, Allantoin lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u00e1ng tin.<\/span><\/p>\n\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"tong-quan-ve-allantoin\"><\/span><b>T\u1ed5ng quan v\u1ec1 Allantoin<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><b>T\u00ean khoa h\u1ecdc \u2013 c\u00e1ch g\u1ecdi kh\u00e1c:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> Allantoin (5-Ureidohydantoin). Kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i acid \u2013 kh\u00f4ng t\u1ea9y da theo ngh\u0129a m\u1ea1nh; thu\u1ed9c nh\u00f3m ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t l\u00e0m d\u1ecbu\/b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 (skin protectant).<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>Ngu\u1ed3n g\u1ed1c khoa h\u1ecdc:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> Ban \u0111\u1ea7u ph\u00e1t hi\u1ec7n trong n\u01b0\u1edbc ti\u1ec3u \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u1eadt c\u00f3 v\u00fa (s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m chuy\u1ec3n ho\u00e1 uric acid), v\u1ec1 sau \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00e1ch t\u1eeb c\u00e2y comfrey (<\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Symphytum officinale<\/span><\/i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">) v\u00e0 hi\u1ec7n nay t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ec3 d\u00f9ng trong m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>L\u1ecbch s\u1eed \u2013 \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> D\u00f9ng l\u00e2u \u0111\u1eddi trong d\u01b0\u1ee3c \u2013 m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m nh\u1edd hai \u0111\u1eb7c t\u00ednh m\u1ea5u ch\u1ed1t: l\u00e0m d\u1ecbu \u2013 gi\u1ea3m kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu v\u00e0 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u00e1i t\u1ea1o l\u1edbp s\u1eebng. Allantoin th\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t trong kem d\u01b0\u1ee1ng ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i, s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m cho da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m, son d\u01b0\u1ee1ng m\u00f4i, after-shave, s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m d\u00e0nh cho em b\u00e9.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_8204\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-8204\" style=\"width: 880px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-8204 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Allantoin-2.webp\" alt=\"Allantoin t\u00e1ch t\u1eeb c\u00e2y comfrey (Symphytum officinale)\" width=\"880\" height=\"550\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Allantoin-2.webp 880w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Allantoin-2-300x300.webp 300w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Allantoin-2-768x480.webp 768w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Allantoin-2-600x375.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 880px) 100vw, 880px\"><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-8204\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Allantoin t\u00e1ch t\u1eeb c\u00e2y comfrey (Symphytum officinale)<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"dac-diem-hoat-chat-allantoin\"><\/span><b>\u0110\u1eb7c \u0111i\u1ec3m ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t Allantoin<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"cong-dung-noi-bat\"><\/span><b>C\u00f4ng d\u1ee5ng n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt\u00a0<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><b>L\u00e0m d\u1ecbu &amp; gi\u1ea3m k\u00edch \u1ee9ng:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> gi\u00fap xoa d\u1ecbu c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c ch\u00e2m ch\u00edch, r\u00e1t nh\u1eb9 do kh\u00f4 \u2013 m\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc \u2013 m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng (gi\u00f3, n\u1eafng, \u0111i\u1ec1u ho\u00e0) ho\u1eb7c khi routine c\u00f3 acid\/retinoid.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>B\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o &amp; gi\u1eef \u1ea9m gi\u00e1n ti\u1ebfp:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 <\/span><b>gi\u1ea3m TEWL<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> (m\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc qua bi\u1ec3u b\u00ec) nh\u1edd t\u0103ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng gi\u1eef n\u01b0\u1edbc c\u1ee7a l\u1edbp s\u1eebng v\u00e0 ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>H\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u00e1i t\u1ea1o da:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng <\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">th\u00fac \u0111\u1ea9y <\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">bong s\u1eebng t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean, nh\u1edd \u0111\u00f3 b\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t tr\u01a1n m\u1ecbn h\u01a1n, t\u0103ng tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i khi thoa actives kh\u00e1c.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>T\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u00edch cao:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> hi\u1ebfm khi g\u00e2y k\u00edch \u1ee9ng; ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p <\/span>m\u1ecdi lo\u1ea1i da<span style=\"font-weight: 400\">, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m, da sau treatment.<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"><br \/>\n<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_8205\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-8205\" style=\"width: 880px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-8205 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Allantoin-3.webp\" alt=\"Allantoin th\u00edch h\u1ee3p cho c\u00e1c l\u00e0n da c\u00f3 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 k\u00edch \u1ee9ng do h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o\" width=\"880\" height=\"550\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Allantoin-3.webp 880w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Allantoin-3-300x300.webp 300w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Allantoin-3-768x480.webp 768w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Allantoin-3-600x375.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 880px) 100vw, 880px\"><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-8205\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Allantoin th\u00edch h\u1ee3p cho c\u00e1c l\u00e0n da c\u00f3 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 k\u00edch \u1ee9ng do h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"co-che-hoat-dong\"><\/span><b>C\u01a1 ch\u1ebf ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><b>Keratolytic nh\u1eb9:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> t\u1ed1i \u01b0u qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh bong s\u1eebng t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean \u2192 l\u1edbp s\u1eebng m\u1ec1m, \u00edt s\u1ea7n; c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c \u201c\u00eam\u201d b\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>\u0110i\u1ec1u bi\u1ebfn vi m\u00f4 vi\u00eam \u2013 k\u00edch \u1ee9ng:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> gi\u1ea3m c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu, \u0111\u1ecf nh\u1eb9 nh\u1edd \u0111\u1eb7c t\u00ednh l\u00e0m d\u1ecbu; kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i thu\u1ed1c kh\u00e1ng vi\u00eam m\u1ea1nh nh\u01b0ng h\u1eefu \u00edch trong ch\u0103m s\u00f3c h\u1eb1ng ng\u00e0y.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>H\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 li\u1ec1n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u00f4ng:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> khuy\u1ebfn kh\u00edch t\u0103ng sinh c\u1ee7a t\u1ebf b\u00e0o s\u1eebng, gi\u00fap ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i v\u00f9ng da b\u1ecb kh\u00f4 n\u1ee9t nh\u1eb9.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"dang-bao-che-thuong-gap\"><\/span><b>D\u1ea1ng b\u00e0o ch\u1ebf th\u01b0\u1eddng g\u1eb7p<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><b>Kem\/gel d\u01b0\u1ee1ng \u1ea9m \u2013 ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> c\u00f4ng th\u1ee9c ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da (th\u01b0\u1eddng k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p: ceramide, cholesterol, FA, glycerin, HA, panthenol).<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>Toner\/essence d\u1ecbu nh\u1eb9:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> t\u0103ng c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c d\u1ec5 ch\u1ecbu sau r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t ho\u1eb7c acid n\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9 th\u1ea5p.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>M\u1eb7t n\u1ea1 gi\u1ea5y\/cream mask:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> l\u00e0m d\u1ecbu nhanh sau n\u1eafng, sau peel nh\u1eb9.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>S\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m body &amp; ch\u0103m s\u00f3c m\u00f4i:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> kem tay g\u00f3t, son d\u01b0\u1ee1ng m\u00f4i, after-sun.<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"><br \/>\n<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"huong-dan-su-dung-allantoin\"><\/span><b>H\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Allantoin<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"doi-tuong-su-dung\"><\/span><b>\u0110\u1ed1i t\u01b0\u1ee3ng s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<figure id=\"attachment_8206\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-8206\" style=\"width: 880px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-8206 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Allantoin-4.webp\" alt=\"\u0110\u1ed1i t\u01b0\u1ee3ng s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Allantoin\" width=\"880\" height=\"550\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Allantoin-4.webp 880w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Allantoin-4-300x300.webp 300w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Allantoin-4-768x480.webp 768w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Allantoin-4-600x375.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 880px) 100vw, 880px\"><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-8206\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">\u0110\u1ed1i t\u01b0\u1ee3ng s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Allantoin<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m, k\u00edch \u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ecf r\u00e1t, da kh\u00f4 m\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc, bong v\u1ea3y l\u1ea5m t\u1ea5m.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Sau treatment nh\u1eb9: AHA\/BHA n\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9 th\u1ea5p, retinoid m\u1edbi l\u00e0m quen, c\u1ea1o r\u00e2u\/wax.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Da d\u00f9ng actives m\u1ea1nh (retinoid, acid, benzoyl peroxide): c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t l\u1edbp \u0111\u1ec7m ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3m kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Da body kh\u00f4 n\u1ee9t, m\u00f4i kh\u00f4, v\u00f9ng c\u1ed5, n\u1ebfp g\u1ea5p, mu b\u00e0n tay c\u1ea7n ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"cach-dung-%e2%80%93-nong-do\"><\/span><b>C\u00e1ch d\u00f9ng \u2013 n\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">N\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9 ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn trong m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m: 0,1\u20130,5%. \u1ede m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da ki\u1ec3u ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 chuy\u00ean s\u00e2u, n\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 cao h\u01a1n tu\u1ef3 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u00f4ng th\u1ee9c.<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"><br \/>\n<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>T\u1ea7n su\u1ea5t:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> 1\u20132 l\u1ea7n\/ng\u00e0y (s\u00e1ng\/t\u1ed1i). C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u00f9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc ho\u1eb7c sau actives \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3m kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu.<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"><br \/>\n<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>Layering g\u1ee3i \u00fd:<\/b><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">R\u1eeda m\u1eb7t d\u1ecbu nh\u1eb9 \u2192 toner Allantoin \u2192 serum \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb (niacinamide\/TXA\/vitC\/retinoid) \u2192 kem d\u01b0\u1ee1ng Allantoin + ceramide.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ng\u00e0y c\u00f3 acid\/retinoid: d\u00f9ng Allantoin <\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">tr\u01b0\u1edbc<\/span><\/i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> ho\u1eb7c <\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">c\u00f4ng th\u1ee9c \u201ck\u1eb9p sandwich\u201d<\/span><\/i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> (kem d\u01b0\u1ee1ng \u2013 active \u2013 kem d\u01b0\u1ee1ng).<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng: c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c d\u1ec5 ch\u1ecbu th\u01b0\u1eddng t\u1ee9c th\u00ec ho\u1eb7c v\u00e0i ng\u00e0y (t\u00f9y thu\u1ed9c c\u00f4ng th\u1ee9c s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m); b\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t m\u1ecbn v\u00e0 \u00edt s\u1ea7n r\u00f5 h\u01a1n sau 2\u20134 tu\u1ea7n d\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ec1u.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"ket-hop-allantoin-sao-cho-hieu-qua\"><\/span><b>K\u1ebft h\u1ee3p Allantoin sao cho hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Allantoin + Panthenol (B5): c\u1eb7p \u0111\u00f4i l\u00e0m d\u1ecbu kinh \u0111i\u1ec3n, gi\u1ea3m \u0111\u1ecf r\u00e1t, ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Allantoin + Ceramide\/Cholesterol\/FA: c\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1 h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o cho da kh\u00f4 \u2013 nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Allantoin + Niacinamide: h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 gi\u1ea3m \u0111\u1ecf nh\u1eb9, t\u1ed1i \u01b0u ho\u00e1 b\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p d\u01b0\u1ee1ng \u1ea9m cho da m\u1ee5n.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Allantoin + AHA\/BHA\/Retinoid: l\u00e0m l\u1edbp \u0111\u1ec7m gi\u1ea3m k\u00edch \u1ee9ng cho da m\u1edbi l\u00e0m quan ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t active m\u1ea1nh; n\u00ean t\u00e1ch l\u1edbp ho\u1eb7c k\u1eb9p gi\u1eefa kem d\u01b0\u1ee1ng.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Allantoin + Zinc PCA\/Madecassoside\/Centella: t\u0103ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng l\u00e0m d\u1ecbu da, h\u1ee3p da m\u1ee5n \u2013 da \u0111\u1ecf.<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"><br \/>\n<\/span><\/p>\n<p>Xem th\u00eam: <a href=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/tinh-chat-phuc-hoi-gsc\/\">Serum ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i GSC<\/a><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"iv-luu-y-chong-chi-dinh-allantoin\"><\/span><b>IV. L\u01b0u \u00fd &amp; Ch\u1ed1ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ecbnh Allantoin<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><b>\u0110\u1ed9 an to\u00e0n cao:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> hi\u1ebfm ghi nh\u1eadn k\u00edch \u1ee9ng\/d\u1ecb \u1ee9ng; tuy v\u1eady, ng\u01b0ng d\u00f9ng n\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ecf r\u00e1t k\u00e9o d\u00e0i b\u1ea5t th\u01b0\u1eddng.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>Kh\u00f4ng t\u1ef1 tr\u1ed9n<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> Allantoin b\u1ed9t v\u00e0o c\u00f4ng th\u1ee9c t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0: \u0111\u1ed9 tan k\u00e9m \u1edf nhi\u1ec7t th\u01b0\u1eddng, d\u1ec5 k\u1ebft tinh \u2013 l\u1ee3n c\u1ee3n n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng gia nhi\u1ec7t v\u00e0 ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t pH.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>Ph\u1ee5 n\u1eef c\u00f3 thai v\u00e0 cho con b\u00fa c\u00f3 d\u00f9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u00f4ng?<\/b><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">C\u00f3. Allantoin d\u00f9ng ngo\u00e0i da \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 an to\u00e0n v\u00e0 ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m. Ch\u1ecdn c\u00f4ng th\u1ee9c \u00edt h\u01b0\u01a1ng li\u1ec7u\/c\u1ed3n, thoa \u0111\u00fang \u2013 \u0111\u1ee7 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. N\u1ebfu da c\u00f3 t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng b\u1ec7nh l\u00fd (ch\u00e0m, vi\u00eam n\u1eb7ng), n\u00ean tham kh\u1ea3o b\u00e1c s\u0129 \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>T\u00e0i li\u1ec7u tham kh\u1ea3o:<\/p>\n<p><i>ALLANTOIN &#8211; Cosmetic Ingredient (INCI)<\/i>. (2024). Specialchem.com. <a href=\"https:\/\/www.specialchem.com\/cosmetics\/inci-ingredients\/allantoin\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">https:\/\/www.specialchem.com\/cosmetics\/inci-ingredients\/allantoin<\/a><\/p>\n<p>\u200c<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Allantoin \u2013 ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t l\u00e0m d\u1ecbu, b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o v\u00e0 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u00e1i t\u1ea1o da; th\u01b0\u1eddng g\u1eb7p trong kem d\u01b0\u1ee1ng, toner, m\u1eb7t n\u1ea1, son d\u01b0\u1ee1ng<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":12,"featured_media":8203,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[1],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-8197","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-su-kien"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/8197","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/12"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=8197"}],"version-history":[{"count":3,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/8197\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":8925,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/8197\/revisions\/8925"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/8203"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=8197"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=8197"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=8197"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}